# Icon bundle placeholder.
#
# Before running `pnpm --filter @marvin/desktop build`, drop a
# 1024x1024 `icon.png` into this directory and run:
#
#     pnpm tauri icon icons/icon.png
#
# That generates icon.icns (macOS) + icon.ico (Windows) + the full PNG
# stack Tauri expects. Kept out of git until the real artwork lands.
